query:
INSERT INTO registered_events (id, chain_id, address, block_safety, event_name, fields_json)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                ON CONFLICT(id) DO UPDATE SET
                    chain_id     = $2,
                    address      = $3,
                    block_safety = $4,
                    event_name   = $5,
                    fields_json  = $6;
